'''Gorkin's Rest''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]]<ref name="CD" /> on [[Wroona/Legends|Wroona]].<ref name="ED" /> In [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]], the cantina was a meeting place for [[Platt Okeefe/Legends|Platt Okeefe]], [[Tru'eb Cholakk]], [[Starter]], [[Dirk Harkness]] and [[Jai Raventhorn]]<ref name="CD">{{JournalCite|1|Chessa's Doom}}</ref> before they launched their sabotage mission against the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] [[Vengeance (Golthan)|''Vengeance'']].<ref name="VS">{{JournalCite|5|Vengeance Strike}}</ref>

